                                Install this module for activate import of Spanish bank statements (Rule 43).<br/>
                                By Spanish Localization Team, Tecnativa, Odoo Community Association (OCA).
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 o_setting_box">
                        <div class="o_setting_left_pane"/>
                        <div class="o_setting_right_pane pb16">
                            <span class="o_form_label">AEAT integration</span>
                            <div class="text-muted">
                                You can install all the AEAT models that you need here.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="o_setting_left_pane">
                            <field name="module_l10n_es_aeat_mod111"/>
